}\n* {{Cite book\n |last=Puig i Boada\n | first=Isidre\n | title=El temple de la Sagrada Fam\u00edlia\n|year=1986\n |editor=Ed. Nou Art Thor, Barcelona\n|isbn=84-7327-135-1\n}}\n* {{Cite book\n |last=Tarragona\n | first=Josep Maria\n | title=Gaud\u00ed, biografia de l'artista\n|year=1999\n |editor=Ed. Proa, Barcelona\n|isbn=84-8256-726-8\n}}\n* {{Cite book\n |last=Van Zandt\n | first=Eleyearr\n | title=La vida y obras de Gaud\u00ed\n|year=1997\n |editor=Asppan\n|isbn=0-7525-1106-8\n}}\n* {{Cite book\n |last=Zerbst\n | first=Rainer\n | title=Gaud\u00ed\n|year=1989\n |editor=Taschen\n|isbn=3-8228-0216-6\n}}\n{{Refend}}\n\n==External links==\n{{Commons category}}\n* [http://www.sagradafamilia.org/en/ Official website of the Construction Board of La Sagrada Fam\u00edlia Foundation]\n*[http://smarthistory.khanacademy.org/gaudi-sagrada-familia.html Gaud\u00ed, Sagrada Fam\u00edlia] (video), [[Smarthistory]]\n<!--========================({{No More Links}})============================\n   | PLEASE BE CAUTIOUS IN ADDING MORE LINKS TO THIS ARTICLE. WIKIPEDIA  |\n   | IS NOT A COLLECTION OF LINKS NOR SHOULD IT BE USED FOR ADVERTISING. |\n   |                                                                     |\n   |           Excessive or inappropriate links WILL BE DELETED.         |\n   | See [[Wikipedia:External links]] & [[Wikipedia:Spam]] for details.  |\n   |                                                                     |\n   | If there are already plentiful links, please propose additions or   |\n   | replacements on this article's discussion page, or submit your link |\n   | to the relevant category at the Open Directory Project (dmoz.org)   |\n   | and link back to that category using the {{dmoz}} template.\n|    =======================({{No More Links}})=============================-->\n\n{{Antoni Gaud\u00ed}}\n{{Barcelona landmarks}}\n{{World Heritage Sites in Spain}}\n{{World Heritage Sites in Catalonia}}\n{{Mathematics and art}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Sagrada Familia}}\n[[Category:Antoni Gaud\u00ed buildings]]\n[[Category:Art Nouveau church buildings in Spain]]\n[[Category:Articles containing video clips]]\n[[Category:Basilica churches in Spain]]\n[[Category:Bien de Inter\u00e9s Cultural landmarks in the Province of Barcelona]]\n[[Category:Buildings and structures under construction in Spain]]\n[[Category:Eixample]]\n[[Category:Hyperboloid structures]]\n[[Category:Mathematics and art]]\n[[Category:Modernisme architecture in Barcelona]]\n[[Category:Roman Catholic churches in Barcelona]]\n[[Category:Skyscrapers in Barcelona]]\n[[Category:Tourist attractions in Barcelona]]\n[[Category:Visionary environments]]\n[[Category:Votive churches]]\n[[Category:World Heritage Sites in Catalonia]]\n", "text_old": "{{About|the basilica||Sagrada Familia (disambiguation)}}\n{{Short description|Cultural property in Barcelona, Catalonia}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=November 2018}}\n{{Infobox religious building\n| name                    = Bas\u00edlica de la Sagrada Fam\u00edlia\n| native_name             = {{native name|ca|Bas\u00edlica de la Sagrada Fam\u00edlia|nbsp=omit|paren=omit}}\n| image                   = \u03a3\u03b1\u03b3\u03c1\u03ac\u03b4\u03b1 \u03a6\u03b1\u03bc\u03af\u03bb\u03b9\u03b1 2941.jpg\n| alt                     =\n| caption                 = Nativity fa\u00e7ade in August 2017\n| map_type                =\n| map_size                =\n| map_caption             =\n| location                = [[Barcelona]], [[Spain]]\n| coordinates             = {{Coord|41|24|13|N|2|10|28|E|type:landmark_region:ES-CT_scale:10000|display=inline,title}}\n| latitude                =\n| longitude               =\n| religious_affiliation   = [[Catholic Church|Roman Catholic]]\n| district                = [[Roman Catholic Archdiocese of Barcelona|Barcelona]]\n| consecration_year       = {{Start date and years ago|df=yes|2010|11|7}}<br /> by [[Pope Benedict XVI|Benedict XVI]]\n<!-- | status                = Expiatory church -->\n| status             